{{see|φιλοσ}}

==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*φίλος / philos / fee'-los

===Etymology===
*Properly dear, that is, a friend; actively fond, that is, friendly (still as a noun, an associate, neighbor, etc.):  

===Noun===
'''φίλος'''

# [[friend]].

